des:
Alexa Skills for the University of Southern Mississippi
A user can ask what year that the University of Southern Mississippi, aka Southern Miss, was established, or a user can ask the skill to tell them facts about Southern Miss.
Currently the fact intent only returns facts related to Southern Miss name changes and the established date.
